ess-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fomega-seiki-mobility-to-give-women-drivers-pink-e-autos-at-lower-prices-125041000266_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20scheme%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20company's%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20(CSR)%20programme%2C%20was%20rolled%20out%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20benefitting%20500%20women%20drivers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Headley's%20Testimony%20Nailed%20Tahawwur%20Rana's%20Role%20Before%20An%20Indian%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETahawwur%20Rana's%20involvement%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20behind%20the%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%20was%20established%20during%20the%20deposition%20of%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20his%20childhood%20friend%20and%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20terror%20attacks%20case.%20In%202016%2C%20Headley%20appeared%20before%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20through%20video%20conference%20from%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20terror%20plot%2C%20who%20had%20visited%20the%20targets%20for%20reconnaissance%2C%20answered%20questions%20from%20Special%20Public%20Prosecutor%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%20and%20defence%20lawyer%20Advocate%20Wahab%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20Rana%20and%20even%20took%20his%20permission%20to%20open%20a%20business%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20a%20front%20for%20his%20activities.%20According%20to%20the%20chargesheet%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%2C%20Rana%20provided%20logistic%2C%20financial%20and%20other%20assistance%20to%20David%20Headley%20and%20others%20involved%20in%20plotting%20terror%20attacks%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20has%20already%20been%20convicted%20in%20the%20US%20for%20his%20links%20to%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%20the%20terror%20group%20that%20plotted%20and%20executed%20the%20attacks%20from%20Pakistan.%20A%20US%20court%20has%20convicted%20him%20of%20helping%20plot%20an%20attack%20against%20a%20Danish%20newspaper%20that%20printed%20cartoons%20of%20Prophet%20Muhammad%2C%20but%20cleared%20him%20of%20the%20charge%20of%20planning%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%20Although%20he%20was%20acquitted%2C%20the%20Chicago%20trial%20brought%20his%20links%20with%20Headley%20into%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20deposition%2C%20Headley%20answered%20Ujjwal%20Nikam's%20questions%20on%20how%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%20were%20planned%20and%20executed.%20His%20statement%20made%20Tawahhur%20Rana's%20role%20very%20clear%2C%20leaving%20no%20room%20for%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US'%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20had%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20Rana's%20conviction%20in%202009%20that%20he%20had%20admitted%20to%20knowing%20that%20Lashkar%20was%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20post-arrest%20statement%20in%20October%202009%2C%20Rana%20admitted%20knowing%20that%20Lashkar%20was%20a%20terrorist%20organization%2C%20and%20that%20Headley%20had%20attended%20training%20camps%20that%20Lashkar%20operated%20in%20Pakistan.%20Headley%20testified%20that%20he%20attended%20the%20training%20camps%20on%20five%20separate%20occasions%20between%202002%20and%202005.%20In%20late%202005%2C%20Headley%20received%20instructions%20from%20members%20of%20Lashkar%20to%20travel%20to%20India%20to%20conduct%20surveillance%2C%20which%20he%20did%20five%20times%2C%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20three%20years%20later%20that%20killed%20more%20than%20160%20people%20and%20wounded%20hundreds%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20early%20summer%20of%202006%2C%20Headley%20and%20two%20Lashkar%20members%20discussed%20opening%20an%20immigration%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20a%20cover%20for%20his%20surveillance%20activities.%20Headley%20testified%20that%20he%20travelled%20to%20Chicago%20and%20advised%20Rana%2C%20his%20long-time%20friend%20since%20the%20time%20they%20attended%20high%20school%20together%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20of%20his%20assignment%20to%20scout%20potential%20targets%20in%20India.%20Headley%20obtained%20approval%20from%20Rana%2C%20who%20owned%20First%20World%20Immigration%20Services%20in%20Chicago%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20to%20open%20a%20First%20World%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20cover%20for%20his%20activities.%20Rana%20directed%20an%20individual%20associated%20with%20First%20World%20to%20prepare%20documents%20supporting%20Headley's%20cover%20story%20and%20advised%20Headley%20how%20to%20obtain%20a%20visa%20for%20travel%20to%20India%2C%20according%20to%20Headley's%20testimony%2C%20as%20well%20as%20e-mails%20and%20other%20documents%20that%20corroborated%20his%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%20corroborated%20these%20details%20when%20he%20testified%20before%20the%20special%20court.%20He%20said%20Lashkar%20had%20planned%20the%20Mumbai%20attack%20and%20the%20same%20group%20of%20ten%20terrorists%20that%20attacked%20Mumbai%20in%20November%202008%20had%20made%20failed%20attempts%20to%20strike%20the%20city%20in%20September%20and%20October%20that%20year.%20David%20Headley%20said%20he%20came%20to%20India%20eight%20times%20before%20the%20attacks%20and%20once%20after.%20He%20spent%20two%20years%20researching%20sites%2C%20even%20taking%20boat%20tours%20around%20the%20city's%20harbour%20and%20befriending%20Bollywood%20stars%20as%20part%20of%20his%20cover.%20Ujjwal%20Nikam%20asked%20Headley%20about%20ISI's%20role%20in%20the%20attacks.%20Headley%20detailed%20how%20he%20met%20two%20ISI%20officers%2C%20Major%20Ali%20and%20Major%20Iqbal%2C%20who%20connected%20him%20to%20Sajid%20Mir%2C%20a%20Lashkar%20recruiter%20with%20known%20links%20to%20the%20ISI.%20Sajid%20Mir%20was%20his%20handler%2C%20but%20he%20also%20mentioned%20%26quot%3Bmy%20other%20Lashkar%20colleagues%26quot%3B.%20Headley%20said%20he%20joined%20the%20Lashkar%20in%202002%20and%20trained%20under%20its%20leaders%20Hafiz%20Saeed%20and%20Zaki-ur%20Rehman%20Lakhvi%2C%20key%20plotters%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%20also%20corroborated%20what%20was%20proven%20in%20the%20trial%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20early%20summer%20of%202006%2C%20Headley%20and%20two%20Lashkar%20members%20discussed%20opening%20an%20immigration%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20a%20cover%20for%20his%20surveillance%20activities.%20Headley%20testified%20that%20he%20travelled%20to%20Chicago%20and%20advised%20Rana%2C%20his%20long-time%20friend%20since%20the%20time%20they%20attended%20high%20school%20together%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20of%20his%20assignment%20to%20scout%20potential%20targets%20in%20India.%20Headley%20obtained%20approval%20from%20Rana%2C%20who%20owned%20First%20World%20Immigration%20Services%20in%20Chicago%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20to%20open%20a%20First%20World%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20cover%20for%20his%20activities.%20Rana%20directed%20an%20individual%20associated%20with%20First%20World%20to%20prepare%20documents%20supporting%20Headley's%20cover%20story%20and%20advised%20Headley%20how%20to%20obtain%20a%20visa%20for%20travel%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%20repeated%20these%20facts%20during%20his%20deposition%20from%20the%20US%C2%A0as%20he%20turned%20approver%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0His%20deposition%20took%20place%20during%20the%20trial%20of%20Abu%20Jundal%2C%20who%20allegedly%20coordinated%20the%20November%202008%20attacks%20from%20a%20control%20room%20in%20Karachi%2C%20Pakistan.%20He%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20tutoring%20the%20terrorists%20in%20language%20during%20their%20training.%20During%20the%20attacks%2C%20Indian%20investigative%20agencies%20had%20found%20one%20voice%20among%20the%20handlers%2C%20who%20were%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20ten%20terrorists%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20to%20have%20an%20identifiable%20Indian%20tone%20and%20accent.%20Investigators%20say%20that%20the%20voice%20was%20of%20Zabiuddin%20Ansari%2C%20who%20uses%20the%20alias%20Abu%20Jundal.%20Ansari%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20Aurangabad%20arms%20haul%20case%20and%20other%20terror%20cases%20as%20well%2C%20according%20to%20the%20investigators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Headley%20Be%20Brought%20Back%20Too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20Headley%2C%20who%20was%20born%20Daood%20Sayed%20Gilani%2C%20is%20in%20a%20US%20prison%20after%20he%20was%20sentenced%20to%2035%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks.%20While%20India%20continues%20to%20push%20for%20his%20extradition%2C%20Assistant%20US%20Attorney%20John%20J%20Lulejian%20told%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20US's%20Los%20Angeles%20that%20unlike%20Rana%2C%20Headley%20had%20immediately%20accepted%20responsibility%20and%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20all%20charges.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20Headley%20fulfilled%20the%20required%20terms%2C%20the%20plea%20agreement%20established%20that%20Headley%20would%20not%20be%20extradited%20to%20India.%20Rana's%20situation%20is%20different%20because%20he%20neither%20pleaded%20guilty%20nor%20cooperated%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20In%202018%2C%20Headley%20was%20seriously%20injured%20in%20a%20prison%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744263840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fi9mgp78c_david-headley-rana_625x300_10_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdavid-headley-tahawwur-rana-26-11-terror-attacks-how-headleys-testimony-nailed-tahawwur-ranas-role-before-an-indian-court-8129705%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tahawwur%20Rana's%20involvement%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20behind%20the%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%20was%20established%20during%20the%20deposition%20of%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20his%20childhood%20friend%20and%20a%20k