%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F04%2F08%2Fus-news%2Fbillion-dollar-tech-firm-stands-by-disgraced-ceo-exposed-for-frequenting-high-end-brothel-in-boston%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20Mr%20Bajpayee%20was%20listed%20among%20numerous%20individuals%20in%20Boston-area%20court%20documents%2C%20accused%20of%20paying%20substantial%20hourly%20rates%20for%20sex%20services%20earlier%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20claim%20that%20Mr%20Bajpayee%20belonged%20to%20an%20exclusive%20group%20of%20clients%2C%20consisting%20of%20doctors%2C%20lawyers%2C%20public%20officials%2C%20and%20government%20contractors.%20The%20probe%20uncovered%20that%20these%20men%20allegedly%20shelled%20out%20as%20much%20as%20%24600%20hourly%20for%20meetings%20with%20mostly%20Asian%20women%2C%20who%20were%20purportedly%20ensnared%20in%20sex%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20calls%20for%20his%20resignation%20from%20some%20employees%2C%20his%20company%2C%20Gradiant%2C%20stood%20by%20him%2C%20issuing%20a%20statement%20expressing%20confidence%20in%20the%20justice%20system%20and%20affirming%20its%20commitment%20to%20its%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20in%20the%20justice%20system%20and%20are%20confident%20that%20this%20will%20resolve%20favorably%20in%20due%20course.%20Unrelated%20to%20this%2C%20Gradiant%20will%20continue%20to%20pursue%20excellence%20in%20technological%20innovation%20and%20to%20strive%20towards%20our%20mission%20to%20ensure%20clean%20water%20for%20all%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%C2%A0Anurag%20Bajpayee%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Bajpayee%20is%20the%20Co-Founder%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20Gradiant%2C%20a%20Boston-based%20company%20specialising%20in%20advanced%20water%20and%20wastewater%20treatment%20solutions.%20Born%20in%20India%2C%20Mr%20Bajpayee%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20cleantech%20industry%2C%20steering%20Gradiant%20from%20its%20origins%20as%20a%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%20spinout%20in%202013%20to%20a%20global%20leader%20valued%20at%20over%20%241%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20company%20addresses%20critical%20water%20challenges%20for%20industries%20such%20as%20semiconductors%2C%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20mining%2C%20and%20food%20and%20beverage%2C%20with%20operations%20spanning%20more%20than%2025%20countries%20and%20over%202%2C500%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajpayee's%20academic%20journey%20began%20at%20La%20Martiniere%20College%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Science%20in%20Mechanical%20Engineering%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Missouri-Columbia%20in%202006.%20He%20then%20pursued%20advanced%20degrees%20at%20MIT%2C%20earning%20a%20Master%20of%20Science%20in%202008%20and%20a%20PhD%20in%20Mechanical%20Engineering%20in%202012.%20His%20doctoral%20research%20focused%20on%20industrial%20desalination%20and%20water%20treatment%2C%20notably%20developing%20a%20membrane-free%20desalination%20technique%20recognized%20by%20Scientific%20American%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BTop%2010%20World-Changing%20Ideas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744260660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F5qu1bm64_anurag-bajpayee_625x300_10_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-anurag-bajpayee-the-indian-origin-ceo-arrested-in-luxury-brothel-scandal-in-us-8129848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20was%20listed%20among%20numerous%20individuals%20in%20Boston-area%20court%20documents%2C%20accused%20of%20paying%20substantial%20hourly%20rates%20for%20sex%20services%20earlier%20in%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20reacts%20after%20