onspiracy%20case%20filed%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20linked%20to%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20attacks%20that%20killed%20166%20people.%20He%20is%20being%20brought%20back%20on%20a%20special%20flight%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20land%20this%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Tahawwur%20Rana%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETahawwur%20Hussain%20Rana%20was%20born%20on%20January%2012%2C%201961%2C%20in%20Chichawatni%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Pakistan.%20He%20studied%20at%20Cadet%20College%20Hasan%20Abdal%2C%20where%20he%20became%20close%20friends%20with%20David%20Headley%2C%20who%20later%20became%20a%20co-conspirator%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks.%20Rana%20joined%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20Medical%20Corps%20and%20served%20as%20a%20captain-general%20duty%20practitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201997%2C%20he%20left%20the%20military%20and%20moved%20to%20Canada%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20doctor.%20Both%20Rana%20and%20his%20wife%20became%20naturalised%20Canadian%20citizens%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20moved%20to%20Chicago%20and%20started%20several%20businesses%2C%20including%20First%20World%20Immigration%20Services%2C%20which%20had%20offices%20in%20Chicago%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Toronto.%20He%20also%20founded%20a%20'Halal%20slaughterhouse'%20that%20processed%20goats%2C%20sheep%2C%20and%20cows%20according%20to%20Islamic%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20owns%20a%20home%20in%20Ottawa%2C%20Canada%2C%20where%20his%20father%20and%20brother%20live.%20His%20father%20was%20a%20school%20principal%20near%20Lahore%2C%20and%20one%20of%20his%20brothers%20is%20a%20psychiatrist%20in%20the%20Pakistani%20military%2C%20while%20another%20is%20a%20journalist%20for%20a%20Canadian%20political%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2064-year-old%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20a%20terror%20plot%20targeting%20the%20Danish%20newspaper%20Jyllands-Posten%20for%20publishing%20cartoons%20of%20Prophet%20M