oice...%26quot%3B%3A%20Michelle%20Obama%20Opens%20Up%20About%20Divorce%20Rumours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20first%20lady%20Michelle%20Obama%20has%20addressed%20her%20reduced%20presence%20in%20public%20and%20at%20political%20events%2C%20saying%20she%20is%20focusing%20on%20her%20well-being%20and%20making%20conscious%20choices%20to%20take%20back%20control%20of%20her%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20actress%20Sophia%20Bush%20on%20the%20Work%20In%20Progress%20podcast%2C%20she%20also%20dismissed%20the%20ongoing%20divorce%20rumours%20with%20Barack%20Obama%20and%20opened%20up%20about%20shifts%20in%20her%20life%20since%20leaving%20the%20White%20House%20eight%20years%20ago.%20With%20her%20daughters%20now%20adults%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20has%20found%20the%20freedom%20to%20reassess%20her%20priorities%20and%20focus%20on%20her%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20absence%20from%20events%20such%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20second%20inauguration%20and%20the%20funeral%20of%20former%20President%20Jimmy%20Carter%20earlier%20this%20year%20prompted%20speculation%20that%20everything%20was%20not%20well%20among%20the%20Obamas.%20The%20most%20persistent%20rumour%20was%20that%20she%20and%20former%20US%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20were%20headed%20for%20a%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20have%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20decisions%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20give%20myself%20that%20freedom.%20Maybe%20even%20as%20much%20as%20I%20let%20my%20kids%20live%20their%20own%20lives%2C%20I%20use%20their%20lives%20as%20an%20excuse%20for%20why%20I%20couldn't%20do%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20as%20per%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F04%2F09%2Fpolitics%2Fmichelle-obama-podcast-divorce-rumors%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Obama%20revealed%20that%20stepping%20away%20from%20cert