as%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%202024%20campaign%20cycle%2C%20backing%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20rally%20in%20Michigan%20before%20the%20election%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BPlease%2C%20please%20do%20not%20hand%20our%20fates%20over%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Trump%2C%20who%20knows%20nothing%20about%20us%2C%20who%20has%20shown%20deep%20contempt%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Obamas%20have%20been%20married%20for%2032%20years%20and%20are%20parents%20to%20two%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744258320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fuuri7nng_barack-obama-michelle-obama_625x300_10_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmichelle-obama-opens-up-about-divorce-rumours-with-barack-obama-i-was-making-a-choice-8129758%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michelle%20Obama%20has%20spoken%20about%20stepping%20back%20from%20political%20events%20and%20shutting%20down%20rumours%20about%20her%20marriage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmichelle-obama-opens-up-about-divorce-rumours-with-barack-obama-i-was-making-a-choice-8129758%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Director%20Ananth%20defends%20'Phule'%20amid%20caste%20controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744258251000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120145804%2Cimgsize-71480.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdirector-ananth-mahadevan-defends-phule-amid-caste-controversy-says-we-dont-get-into-a-film-with-these-kinds-of-doubts-and-fears-in-mind%2Farticleshow%2F120145733.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F120145733.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%221