th%201307%20runs%2C%20behind%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shaun%20Marsh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F890-shaun-marsh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShaun%20Marsh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%201338%20runs.%20After%20Sai%2C%20there%20are%20some%20heavyweights%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Chris%20Gayle%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F199-chris-gayle-playerprofile%5C%22%3EChris%20Gayle%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1141)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kane%20Williamson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1058-kane-williamson-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKane%20Williamson%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1096)%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Matthew%20Hayden%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F219-matthew-hayden-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Hayden%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1082).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudharsan%20is%20also%20the%20only%20Indian%20in%20IPL's%20history%20to%20score%20five%20back-to-back%2050%2B%20scores%20at%20a%20venue.%20In%20GT's%20last%20two%20IPL%202024%20matches%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20Sudharsan%20hit%20an%20unbeaten%2084%20and%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20knock%20and%20the%20conditions%2C%20Sai%20said%20the%20pitch%20was%20initially%20challenging%20but%20eventually%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20ideal%20for%20stroke%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20surface%20was%20swinging%20a%20bit%20at%20the%20start%2C%20but%20the%20wicket%20was%20good%20to%20bat%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Archer)%20started%20well%2C%20but%20we%20consolidated%20after.%20We%20understood%20the%20wicket%20was%20really%20good%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20push%20a%20bit%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGT's%20innings%20had%20the%20foundation%20of%20smart%20planning%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20pacing%20the%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20we%20were%20going%2C%20we%20felt%20we%20could%20get%2015%20more%2C%20but%20this%20is%20still%20a%20great%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20personal%20approach%20and%20whether%20he%20aims%20for%20consistency%2C%20the%20left-hander%20replied%20modestly%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20trying%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20any%20way%2C%20just%20reacting%20to%20the%20situation%20and%20doing%20the%20best%20out%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20also%20offered%20insights%20on%20the%20pace%20challenge%20posed%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jofra%20Archer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64664-jofra-archer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJofra%20Archer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20faced%20Nortje%20last%20year%2C%20but%20he%20was%20probably%20quicker.%20Jofra%20got%20a%20bit%20of%20purchase%20off%20the%20wicket%20today.%20Slower%20ones%20and%20change%20of%20pace%20will%20hold%20on%20the%20wicket%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20we%20have%20a%20good%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20dew%20unlikely%20to%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20as%20Sai%20believes%2C%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20have%20their%20task%20cut%20out.%20Chasing%20down%20218%20under%20pressure%20at%20a%20venue%20like%20Ahmedabad%20is%20no%20small%20feat%2C%20and%20GT%20will%20be%20banking%20on%20their%20bowlers%20to%20seal%20the%20game%20after%20their%20batters%20set%20the%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744257780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F7q43n4r_sai-sudharshan-_625x300_03_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fsai-sudharsan-shatters-record-books-becomes-first-indian-ever-in-ipl-to-8127895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sai%20Sudharsan%20delivered%20a%20commanding%20performance%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20smashing%2082%20off%20just%2053%20balls%20as%20GT%20posted%20a%20formidable%20217%2F6%20against%20RR%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engag