20hours%20ago.%20According%20to%20Trump%2C%20who%20had%20introduced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-announces-90-day-pause-on-tariffs-for-most-countries-8127497%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslew%20of%20tariffs%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20address%20the%20alleged%20trade%20imbalance%20with%20the%20US%2C%20over%2075%20countries%20had%20negotiated%20and%20not%20retaliated%20against%20him%20-%20which%20led%20to%20the%20pause.%20During%20the%2090%20days%2C%20a%20significantly%20reduced%20reciprocal%20tariff%20of%20just%2010%20per%20cent%20would%20be%20in%20effect%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20China%2C%20however%2C%20Trump%20announced%20an%20immediate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-raises-tariffs-on-china-to-125-after-beijings-84-move-earlier-today-8127464%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20in%20tariffs%20on%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20125%20per%20cent%2C%20up%20from%20the%20previously%20declared%20104%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20respect%20that%20China%20has%20shown%20to%20the%20World's%20Markets%2C%20I%20am%20hereby%20raising%20the%20Tariff%20charged%20to%20China%20by%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20to%20125%25%2C%20effective%20immediately.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20hopefully%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20China%20will%20realize%20that%20the%20days%20of%20ripping%20off%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20sustainable%20or%20acceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20wants%20to%20make%20a%20deal.%20They%20just%20don't%20know%20how%20quite%20to%20go%20about%20it...President%C2%A0Xi%20Jinping%20is%20a%20proud%20man.%20They%20don't%20know%20quite%20how%20to%20go%20about%20it%2C%20but%20they'll%20figure%20it%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20did%20Trump%20hit%20a%20pause%20on%20tariffs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20days%2C%20fellow%20Republicans%20and%20business%20executives%20had%20been%20insisting%20the%20US%20President%20to%20stop%20the%20tariffs%2C%20given%20the%20fear%20of%20a%20major%20trade%20war%2C%20triggering%20a%20global%20market%20meltdown%2C%20and%20raising%20concerns%20of%20a%20looming%20global%20recession.%20However%2C%20he%20stayed%20put%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20policies%20will%20never%20change%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Wednesday%2C%20it%20had%20become%20clear%20that%20the%20campaign%20to%20convince%20Trump%20to%20go%20back%20on%20the%20tariffs%20would%20not%20change%20as%20they%20had%20come%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20growing%20alarm%20inside%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20over%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20bond%20market%20was%20the%20only%20factor%20that%20made%20Trump%20hit%20a%20pause%20on%20his%20reciprocal%20tariff%20regime%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F04%2F09%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-tariffs-retreat-bond-market%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20US%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20raised%20the%20concerns%20to%20Trump%2C%20while%20White%20House%20economic%20officials%20briefed%20him%20on%20the%20accelerating%20selloff%20in%20the%20US%20Treasury%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20addressed%20reporters%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20pause%20on%20tariffs%20-%20it%20indicated%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20more%20of%20an%20impulse-driven%20one%20rather%20than%20a%20mapped-out%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bond%20market%20is%20very%20tricky%2C%20I%20was%20watching%20it.%20The%20bond%20market%20right%20now%20is%20beautiful.%20But%20yeah%2C%20I%20saw%20last%20night%20where%20people%20were%20getting%20a%20little%20queasy.%20We%20didn't%20have%20access%20to%20lawyers%2C%20or%20it%20was%20just%20wrote%20up.%20We%20wrote%20it%20up%20from%20our%20hearts%2C%20right%3F%20It%20was%20written%20from%20the%20heart%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it%20was%20well%20written%20too%2C%20but%20it%20was%20written%20from%20the%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20that%20people%20were%20jumping%20a%20little%20bit%20out%20of%20line...They%20were%20getting%20yippie%2C%20you%20know%2C%20they%20were%20getting%20a%20little%20bit%20a%20little%20bit%20afraid.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20flexible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20stocks%20surged%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20stocks%20rocketed%20higher%20on%20Wednesday%20following%20Trump's%20shock%20move%20to%20pause%20many%20new%20tariffs%2C%20lifting%20an%20equity%20market%20beaten%20down%20by%20days%20of%20losses%20amid%20rising%20recession%20worries.%20Within%20moments%20of%20the%20announcement%2C%20the%20Dow%20index%20surged%20ahead%20around%202%2C500%20points%20along%20the%20way%20to%20a%20nearly%20eight-percent%20gain%20on%20the%20session.%20While%2C%20the%20tech-rich%20Nasdaq%20gained%2012.2%20percent%20to%20notch%20its%20best%20day%20in%2024%20years%2C%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20surged%206.0%20percent%20higher%20to%205%2C281.44%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20jumped%20more%20than%20four%20percent%2C%20while%20the%20dollar%20also%20strengthened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Trump%20imposed%20a%2026%20per%20cent%20customised%20reciprocal%20tariff%20on%20Indian%20imports%2C%20the%20Indian%20markets%20have%20taken%20a%20plunge.%20However%2C%20with%20the%2090-day%20pause%2C%20the%20stocks%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20breather%2C%20with%20New%20Delhi%20getting%20more%20time%20to%20work%20on%20the%20deal%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinistry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20that%20reciprocal%20tariffs