rrently%20operates%20the%20MiG-29K%20fighter%20jets%20for%20its%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%20-%20INS%20Vikrant%20and%20INS%20Vikramaditya.%20The%20Navy%20will%20induct%2026%20Rafale-M%20fighter%20jets%20-%2022%20single-seater%20fighters%20and%20four%20double-seater%20trainer%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BRafale%20-%20A%20Kinetic%20Push%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20of%20Naval%20Staff%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fi-was-captain-of-ins-viraat-now-it-will-become-scrap-2290271%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdmiral%20Arun%20Prakash%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20on%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%2C%20explaining%20how%20it%20will%20add%20a%20%26quot%3Bkinetic%20push%20in%20the%20Navy's%20striking%20power%26quot%3B.%20The%20former%20Navy%20chief%20also%20spoke%20on%20Chinese%20aircraft%20carrier%20deployments%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20on%20the%20debate%20over%20whether%20aircraft%20carriers%20are%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20attacks%20than%20they%20have%20ever%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20about%20what%20the%20Rafale%20addition%20means%20for%20the%20Navy%2C%20Admiral%20Prakash%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20add%20a%20huge%20punch%2C%20kinetic%20punch%20to%20Indian%20Navy's%20striking%20power%20in%20many%20dimensions%2C%20air%20defense%2C%20anti-shipping%20strike%2C%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20you%20name%20it.%20The%20Rafale%20is%20a%20fine%20and%20capable%20aircraft.%20It's%20a%20welcome%20addition.%20The%20Rafale%20is%20probably%20half%20a%20generation%20or%20a%20generation%20ahead%20of%20the%20MiG-29K.%20So%20it's%20going%20to%20add%20a%20punch%20to%20the%20fleet%20at%20sea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20follow-up%20question%20on%20how%20it%20adds%20a%20punch%20to%20the%20fighter%20fleet%2C%20Admiral%20Prakash%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20MiG-29K%20was%20an%20adaptation%20of%20a%20land-based%20fighter%2C%20the%20MiG-29.%20And%20when%20we%20got%20it%2C%20it%20was%20virtually%20in%20a%20prototype%20state.%20It%20took%20a%20few%20years%20to%20sort%20out%20all%20the%20bugs%20to%20achieve%20stable%20operations.%20But%20the%20Rafale%20comes%20about%2010%20years%20after%20the%20MiG-29.%20So%20it's%20electronics%2C%20it's%20data%20fusion%2C%20and%20the%20weapons%20it%20carries%20will%20certainly%20make%20it%20a%20more%20capable%20aircraft%20than%20the%20MiG-29.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20certainly%20add%20to%20the%20kinetic%20punch%20of%20the%20fleet%20at%20sea%2C%20to%20the%20aircraft%20carriers.%20When%20we%20acquired%20the%20Vikramaditya%20and%20the%20Vikrant%2C%20we%20hadn't%20factored%20in%20the%20acquisition%20of%20the%20Rafale%2C%20or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20any%20other%20fighter%20other%20than%20the%20MiG-29K%2C%20perhaps%20the%20Tejas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20operates%2036%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20in%20two%20squadrons%20-%20%C2%A0The%2017%20Squadron%20(the%20Golden%20Arrows)%20and%20the%20101%20Squadron%20(The%20Falcons)%2C%20based%20in%20Ambala%20and%20Hashimara%2C%20respectively.%20The%204.5%20generation%20multi-role%20fighter%20aircraft%20is%20capable%20of%20conducting%20all%20combat%20aviation%20missions%20like%20air%20superiority%2C%20close-air-support%2C%20ground%20attack%20missions%2C%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20manufacturer%2C%20Dassault%20Aviation%2C%20all%20the%20variants%20-%20Rafale%20C%20(Air%20Force)%20and%20Rafale-M%20(Marine)%20have%20the%20maximum%20airframe%20and%20equipment%20commonality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'MiG-29%20Was%20A%20Hobson's%20Choice%20For%20Us'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Prakash%2C%20who%20was%20closely%20involved%20during%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20INS%20Vikramaditya%2C%20further%20explained%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20MiG-29%20into%20the%20Navy%20and%20said%20it%20was%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BHobson's%20choice%20for%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Vikramaditya%20was%20a%20Kiev-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20and%20was%20named%20Admiral%20Gorshkov%20in%20Russia.%20The%20acquisition%20of%20Gorshkov%20had%20been%20under%20consideration%20since%201994%2C%20and%2010%20years%20later%2C%20in%202004%2C%20a%20deal%20was%20signed%20between%20India%20and%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Arun%20Prakash%20oversaw%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20into%20the%20Navy.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%20former%20Navy%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20negotiating%20for%20the%20Gorshkov%2C%20which%20later%20became%20the%20Vikramaditya.%20That%20was%20the%20late%201990s.%20Then%2C%20firstly%2C%20there%20were%20no%20ski-jump%20capable%20aircraft%20available%20other%20than%20the%20Sea%20Harrier%2C%20which%20we%20already%20had.%20And%20the%20Russians%20were%20just%20developing%20the%20MiG-29%20and%20the%20Sukhoi-27.%20We%20went%20to%20the%20French%3B%20we%20sent%20a%20team%20to%20France%20to%20evaluate%20the%20Rafale%2C%20and%20they%20said%2C%20Sorry%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20we%20cannot%20offer%20you%20the%20Rafale-M.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20those%20days%2C%20the%20political%20situation%20did%20not%20allow%20us%20to%20even%20contemplate%20acquiring%2C%20say%2C%20an%20F-18%20or%20something.%20Of%20course%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20F-18%20had%20not%20been%20proved%20off%20the%20ski-jump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20choices%20were%20limited.%20And%20then%2C%20when%20we%20started%20negotiating%20for%20the%20Vikramaditya-Gorshkov%2C%20the%20MiG-29%20was%20more%20or%20less%20a%20Hobson's%20choice%20for%20us.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20take%20it.%20It's%20only%20subsequently%20that%20the%20Americans%20offered%20the%20F-18%3B%20they%20proved%20it%20off%20the%20ski-jump%2C%20the%20French%20proved%20the%20Rafale%20off%20the%20ski-jump%2C%20and%20they%20came%20to%20India%20to%20go%20out%20to%20do%20it.%20And%20then%20we%20had%20these%20options%20available.%26quot%3B%20The%20MiG-29K%20fighter%20jets%20were%20inducted%20into%20the%20Naval%20fighter%20fleet%20in%202013%2C%20and%20in%202016%2C%20India%20phased%20out%20the%20last%20remaining%20Sea%20Harriers%20after%20almost%2030%20years%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Boeing%20F%2FA-18%20Super%20Hornet%20underwent%20operational%20demonstration%20tests%20at%20the%20ski-jump%20facility%20at%20INS%20Hansa%20in%20Goa%20in%202022.%20However%2C%20with%20India's%20decision%20to%20opt%20for%20the%20Rafale%2C%20the%20US%20fighter%20jet%20failed%20to%20secure%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20or%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Prakash%20said%20the%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20will%20be%20an%20addition%20to%20the%20naval%20variant%20of%20the%20India-made%20Tejas%20fighter%20jet%2C%20which%20is%20still%20in%20trials%20for%20the%20sea%20and%20the%20future%20Twin%20Engine%20Deck%20Based%20Fighter%20(TEDBF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202015%20report%2C%20the%20Comptroller%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20highlighted%20issues%20with%20the%20MiG-29K's%20airframe%2C%20its%20RD%20MK-33%20engine%20and%20its%20fly-by-wire%20system%2C%20and%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BAircraft%20were%20being%20technically%20accepted%20despite%20having%20discrepancies%2Fanomalies.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChinese%20Threat%20In%20The%20Indian%20Ocean%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20Chinese%20carrier%20battle%20groups%20deploy%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%2C%20Admiral%20Prakash%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20we've%20not%20seen%20a%20Chinese%20task%20force%20cruising%20around%20in%20our%20waters%20is%20because%20they%20lack%20air%20cover%2C%20integral%20air%20cover.%20But%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20have%20three%20aircraft%2C%20they've%20already%20got%20two%2C%20and%20a%20third%20one%20is%20doing%20trials.%20But%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20can%20spare%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20air%20cover%2C%20organic%20air%20cover%20to%20their%20forces%2C%20maritime%20forces%2C%20I%20do%20not%20doubt%20that%20they%20will%20put%20in%20an%20appearance%20in%20our%20waters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20they've%20got%20birthing%20facilities%20in%20Djibouti%2C%20where%20they%20set%20up%20their%20first%20overseas%20base%2C%20means%20that%20they've%20got%20logistic%20support%20of%20their%20own%2C%20not%20just%20in%20Pakistan%20(Gwadar%20port)%2C%20which%20is%20an%20ally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20commissioned%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%20-%20Liaoning%20and%20Shandong%20-%20the%20former%20is%20a%20Soviet-era%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20which%20Beijing%20commissioned%20in%202012%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20is%20its%20first%20domestically%20built%20carrier.%20The%20third%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20Fujian%2C%20is%20China's%20largest%20and%20most%20advanced%20aircraft%20carrier%20ever%20built%2C%20with%20a%20potent%20aircraft%20launching%20system.%20Fujian%20underwent%20sea%20trials%20and%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20commissioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Defence%2C%20in%20its%20latest%20report%20on%20Chinese%20naval%20modernization%2C%20said%20Beijing%20is%20reportedly%20building%20a%20fourth%20aircraft%20carrier%20similar%20to%20Fujian%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20nuclear-powered%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Prakash%20said%20if%20China%20comes%20into%20our%20waters%2C%20then%20the%20nearest%20base%20is%20at%20least%203%2C000%20nautical%20miles%20away%20in%20Hainan%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20extended%20logistical%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0Chain%20for%20them.%20So%20if%20a%20need%20arises%20for%20them%20for%20technical%20assistance%20and%20logistical%20support%2C%20then%20%26quot%3BDjibouti%20is%20a%20great%20reassurance%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Chinese%20Navy%20and%20%26quot%3Bif%20they%20get%20Gwadar%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20bonus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAircraft%20Carriers%20More%20Vulnerable%20To%20Attacks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Arun%20Prakash%20was%20a%20naval%20aviator%20and%20a%20gallantry%20award%20recipient.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20two%20pilots%20who%20were%20deputed%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20during%20the%201971%20war%2C%20where%20he%20flew%20the%20Hawker%20Hunters%20and%20was%20awarded%20a%20Vir%20Chakra%20for%20action%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Prakash%20disagreed%20with%20the%20argument%20that%20aircraft%20carriers%20are%20vulnerable%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20attacks%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%20in%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-over-150-chinese-citizens-fighting-for-russia-in-ukraine-claims-volodymyr-zelensky-8128207%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia-Ukraine%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20drone%20attacks%20from%20Houthis%20on%20naval%20platforms%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20inherently%2C%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20is%20possibly%20the%20most%20protected%20warship%20there%20is.%20It%20has%20its%20fighter%20cover.%20It%20has%20radar%20coverage.%20It%20has%20anti-submarine%20helicopters.%20So%2C%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20protects%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20fleet.%20It's%20the%20wrong%20logic%20to%20think%20that%20it%20needs%20escorts.%20It%20does%20need%20escorts%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20mutual%20sort%20of%20relationship.%20And%20I%20think%20we%20must%20focus%20on%20the%20recent%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Navy%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20the%20Houthis%20have%20been%20firing%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20capable%20those%20missiles%20are%2C%20at%20American%20aircraft%20carriers.%20They've%20all%20been%20shot%20down.%20No%20US%20Navy%20carrier%20has%20so%20far%20been%20affected%20by%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecondly%2C%20Iran%20launched%20a%20few%20hundred%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%20Most%20of%20those%20missiles%20were%20shot%20down%2C%20not%20just%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20but%20by%20US%20Navy%20ships%20which%20were%20parked%20in%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean.%20Their%20anti-ballistic%20missile%20defense%20shot%20down%20most%20of%20the%20ballistic%20missiles%20fired%20by%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20scare%20of%20aircraft%20carriers%20being%20overly%20susceptible%20to%20missile%20attacks%20has%20now%2C%20I%20think%2C%20been%20more%20or%20less%20proved%20otherwise.%20Aircraft%20carriers%20can%20defend%20themselves...So%2C%20let's%20not%20frighten%20ourselves%20overly%20about%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20aircraft%20carriers.%20They%20have%20so%20much%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Admiral%20Prakash%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744248840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F322l3tl8_rafale_625x300_13_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-ex-navy-chief-arun-prakash-on-rafale-jets-and-chinese-threat-in-indian-ocean-8129116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Chief%20of%20Naval%20Staff%2C%20Admiral%20Arun%20Prakash%2C%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20on%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%2C%20explaining%20how%20it%20will%20add%20a%20%26quot%3Bkinetic%20push%20in%20the%20Navy's%20striking%20power%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-ex-navy-chief-arun-prakash-on-rafale-jets-and-chinese-threat-in-indian-ocean-8129116%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Water%20To%20Cost%20More%20In%20Bengaluru%20From%20Today%20As%20Board%20Revises%20Tariffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengaluru%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB)%20is%20set%20to%20revise%20water%20tariffs%20to%20offset%20its%20ever%20growing%20expenditure%2C%20said%20Chairman%20Ram%20Prasath%20Manohar%20on%20Wednesday.%20An%20official%20order%20notifying%20the%20new%20rates%20will%20be%20issued%20on%20April%2010%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20at%20the%20BWSSB%20headquarters%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Manohar%20said%20Bengaluru%20has%20witnessed%20rapid%20growth%20in%20both%20population%20and%20geographic%20spread%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBWSSB%2C%20an%20autonomous%20body%20without%20government%20subsidies%2C%20relies%20heavily%20on%20water%20charges%20as%20its%20primary%20source%20of%20revenue%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20electricity%20costs%20have%20risen%20by%20107%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20maintenance%20expenses%20have%20increased%20by%20122.5%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20despite%20a%20monthly%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore%2C%20the%20Board%20currently%20collects%20only%20Rs%20120%20crore%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20monthly%20deficit%20of%20Rs%2080%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20bridge%20this%20financial%20gap%20and%20improve%20service%20delivery%2C%20a%20rational%20and%20modest%20tariff%20revision%20has%20been%20proposed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Manohar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20domestic%20category%2C%20the%20proposed%20tariff%20hike%20includes%20an%20increase%20of%200.15%20paise%20per%20litre%2C%20for%20up%20to%208%2C000%20litres.%20For%208%2C001%20to%2025%2C000%20litres%2C%20an%20increase%20of%200.30%20paise%20per%20litre%20and%20between%2025%2C001%20and%2050%2C000%20litres%2C%20an%20increase%20of%200.80%20paise%20per%20litre%20and%20above%2050%2C001%20litres%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20Re%201%20per%20litre%20are%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20high-rise%20domestic%20buildings%2C%20till%202%2C00%2C000%20litres%2C%20an%20increase%20of%200.30%20paise%20per%20litre%20is%20proposed.%20While%202%2C00%2C001%20to%205%2C00%2C000%20litres%2C%20will%20see%20an%20increase%20of%200.60%20paise%20per%20litre%20and%20above%205%2C00%2C001%20litres%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20Re%201%20per%20litre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20non-domestic%20usage%2C%20a%20flat%20hike%20of%200.90%20paise%20per%20litre%20is%20proposed%20for%20bulk%20usage.%20While%20up%20to%2010%2C000%20litres%20will%20cost%20Re%201%20per%20litre%20more%20and%20from%2010%2C001%20to%2025%2C000%20litres%2C%20Rs%201.30%20per%20litre.%20Between%2025%2C001%20and%2050%2C000%20litres%2C%20an%20increase%20of%201.50%20paise%20per%20litre%20is%20proposed.%20For%2050%2C001%20to%2075%2C000%20litres%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20increase%20of%201.90%20paise%20per%20litre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%2075%2C001%20to%201%2C00%2C000%20litres%2C%20the%20hike%20is%20only%20Rs%201.10%20per%20litre%20and%20above%201%2C00%2C000%20litres%2C%20it%20is%20Rs%201.20%20paise%20per%20litre%2C%20said%20Manohar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20following%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Administrative%20Reforms%20Commission%2C%20BWSSB%20has%20decided%20to%20adopt%20an%20annual%203%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20water%20tariff%20starting%20April%201%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revised%20tariff%20will%20reflect%20in%20bills%20issued%20from%20May%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744248840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fhqhqjqd_water-generic_625x300_11_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwater-to-cost-more-in-bengaluru-from-tomorrow-as-board-revises-tariffs-8127343%22%2C%22