.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20levies%20came%20into%20force%2C%20Beijing's%20Commerce%20Minister%20had%20said%20the%20%E2%80%98reciprocal%20tariffs'%20by%20the%20US%20are%20%E2%80%9Ca%20serious%20infringement%20of%20the%20legitimate%20interests%20of%20all%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20a%20Xinhua%20report%2C%20an%20official%20from%20the%20Ministry%20earlier%20said%20that%20no%20one%20would%20win%20in%20a%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20emphasize%20that%20there%20is%20no%20winner%20in%20a%20trade%20war%2C%20and%20that%20China%20does%20not%20want%20a%20trade%20war.%20But%20the%20Chinese%20government%20will%20by%20no%20means%20sit%20by%20when%20the%20legitimate%20rights%20and%20interests%20of%20its%20people%20are%20being%20hurt%20and%20deprived%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20U%20Turn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20turnabout%2C%20which%20came%20less%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20steep%20new%20tariffs%20kicked%20in%20on%20most%20trading%20partners%2C%20followed%20the%20most%20intense%20episode%20of%20financial%20market%20volatility%20since%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20The%20upheaval%20erased%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20from%20stock%20markets%20and%20led%20to%20an%20unsettling%20surge%20in%20U.S.%20government%20bond%20yields%20that%20appeared%20to%20catch%20Trump's%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20that%20people%20were%20jumping%20a%20little%20bit%20out%20of%20line%2C%20they%20were%20getting%20yippy%2C%20you%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20American%20President%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20announcement%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20golf%20term.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20returning%20to%20the%20White%20House%20in%20January%2C%20the%20Republican%20billionaire%20has%20repeatedly%20threatened%20an%20array%20of%20punitive%20measures%20on%20trading%20partners%2C%20only%20to%20revoke%20some%20of%20them%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20The%20on-again%2C%20off-again%20approach%20has%20baffled%20world%20leaders%20and%20spooked%20business%20executives.%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20had%20been%20considering%20a%20pause%20for%20several%20days.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20White%20House%20denounced%20a%20report%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20considering%20such%20a%20move%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bfake%20news.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20reversal%20of%20the%20country-specific%20tariffs%20is%20not%20absolute.%20A%2010%20per%20cent%20blanket%20duty%20on%20almost%20all%20US%20imports%20will%20remain%20in%20effect%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%20The%20announcement%20also%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20affect%20duties%20on%20autos%2C%20steel%20and%20aluminum%20that%20are%20already%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2090-day%20freeze%20also%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20duties%20paid%20by%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20because%20their%20goods%20are%20still%20subject%20to%2025%20per%20cent%20fentanyl-related%20tariffs%20if%20they%20do%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20US-Mexico-Canada%20trade%20agreement's%20rules%20of%20origin.%20Those%20duties%20remain%20in%20place%20for%20the%20moment%2C%20with%20an%20indefinite%20exemption%20for%20USMCA-compliant%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BBe%20Flexible'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day's%20events%20cast%20into%20stark%20relief%20the%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20Trump's%20policies%20and%20how%20he%20and%20his%20team%20create%20and%20implement%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20asserted%20that%20the%20pullback%20had%20been%20the%20plan%20all%20along%20to%20bring%20countries%20to%20the%20bargaining%20table.%20Trump%2C%20though%2C%20later%20indicated%20that%20the%20near-panic%20in%20markets%20that%20had%20unfolded%20since%20his%20April%202%20announcements%20had%20factored%20in%20to%20his%20thinking.%20Despite%20insisting%20for%20days%20that%20his%20policies%20would%20never%20change%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20on%20%C2%A0Wednesday%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20flexible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'China%20Unlikely%20To%20Change%20Strategy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20believe%20that%20while%20Trump's%20new%20strategy%20will%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20many%20nations%2C%20Beijing%20is%20unlikely%20to%20change%20its%20strategy%20and%20back%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20unlikely%20to%20change%20its%20strategy%3A%20stand%20firm%2C%20absorb%20pressure%2C%20and%20let%20Trump%20overplay%20his%20hand.%20Beijing%20believes%20Trump%20sees%20concessions%20as%20a%20weakness%2C%20so%20giving%20ground%20only%20invites%20more%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniel%20Russel%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20international%20security%20and%20diplomacy%20at%20the%20Asia%20Society%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20countries%20will%20welcome%20the%2090-day%20stay%20of%20execution%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20lasts%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20whiplash%20from%20constant%20zigzags%20creates%20more%20of%20the%20uncertainty%20that%20businesses%20and%20governments%20hate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump%20indicated%20a%20resolution%20with%20China%20was%20possible%20as%20well.%20But%20officials%20have%20said%20they%20will%20prioritize%20talks%20with%20other%20countries.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20wants%20to%20make%20a%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20just%20don't%20know%20how%20quite%20to%20go%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744248480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F7lethq9g_trump-tariffs_625x300_10_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhite-house-warns-after-donald-trumps-125-percent-tariffs-on-china-do-not-retaliate-812