%20some%20high%20school%20graduates.%20Business%20Insider%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-kids-birth-rates-rising-costs-student-loan-debt-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20spoke%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20millennial%20moms%20who%20want%20kids%20but%20can't%20afford%20them%20due%20to%20student%20debt%20and%20rising%20childcare%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Gloria%20Johnson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20an%20educator%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20really%20important%20that%20we%20teach%20the%20characteristics%20and%20the%20skills%20that%20kids%20are%20going%20to%20need%20to%20be%20successful.%20We%20can't%20teach%20them%20to%20be%20privileged.%20We%20can't%20teach%20them%20that%20they%20have%20to%20bend%20these%20circumstances%20to%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETennessee%20Sen.%20Janice%20Bowling%2C%20who%20sponsored%20the%20Senate%20version%20of%20the%20bill%20that%20passed%20last%20week%2C%20said%20on%20the%20Senate%20floor%20that%20she's%20aware%20that%20not%20everyone%20gets%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20people%20that%20are%20very%20dear%20that%20went%20to%20college%2C%20got%20their%20degree%2C%20never%20married%2C%20and%20they%20live%20very%20successful%2C%20happy%20lives%2C%20but%20if%20it's%20in%20your%20purview%20to%20get%20married%2C%20then%20you%20need%20to%20get%20married%20and%20then%20have%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETennessee's%20bill%20now%20heads%20to%20the%20governor's%20desk%20to%20be%20signed%20into%20law%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20will%20take%20effect%20for%20the%202026-27%20school%20year.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOther%20states%20have%20also%20introduced%20similar%20bills%20%E2%80%94%20Ohio%2C%20Utah%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20and%20Mississippi%20are%20among%20the%20states%20pushing%20to%20get%20the%20success%20sequence%20taught%20in%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20about%20the%