tting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20work%20on%20movies%20of%20that%20scale%20could%20potentially%20%E2%80%94%20and%20seems%20like%20it's%20working%2C%20knock%20on%20wood%20%E2%80%94%20get%20me%20access%20to%20different%20types%20of%20roles%20in%20smaller%20movies.%20And%20that%20was%20something%20that%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20succeeded%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou've%20played%20not%20one%2C%20but%20two%20Marvel%20characters%2C%20Maggie%20in%20%26quot%3BAnt-Man%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20also%20voicing%20War%20Pig%20in%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguardians-of-the-galaxy-vol-3-cameos-celebrities-appearances-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuardians%20of%20the%20Galaxy%20Vol.%203%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20so%20random.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20random%20because%20I'm%20friends%20with%20James%20Gunn%2C%20so%20I%20was%20excited%20that%20he%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20would%20you%20want%20to%20do%20this%20one%20weird%20thing%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20just%20about%20to%20ask%2C%20how%20did%20you%20come%20to%20play%20a%20re-engineered%20cyborg%20pig%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20bucket%20list%20item%20for%20me%2C%20definitely.%20When%20thinking%20about%20how%20many%20cyborg%20pigs%20are%20there%20to%20play%20and%20how%20many%20opportunities%E2%80%A6%20I'm%20kidding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20movies%20and%2C%20obviously%2C%20the%20Marvel%20Universe%2C%20so%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20come%20in.%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20tell%20anyone%2C%20so%20it%20was%20also%20fun%20to%20keep%20a%20secret%20for%20a%20little%20while%20until%20the%20movie%20came%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22513d9f37-6e6e-41e0-adab-72a68efe718f%5C%22%3EOn%20wishing%20her%20acting%20school%20gave%20business%20advice%20and%20th