%20the%20reforestation%20projects%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-8-1744205295.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-8-1744205295-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-8-1744205295-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-8-1744205295-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-8-1744205295-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418900%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20re-introduction%20of%20native%20plant%20species%20is%20focused%20upon%20during%20the%20reforestation%20projects%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Aravalli%20range%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20fold%20mountains%20in%20India%20and%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20protecting%20the%20NCR%20region%20from%20desertification.%20The%20plant%20has%20degraded%20much%20of%20the%20Aravalli%20landscape%20and%20years%20of%20degradation%20have%20weakened%20its%20natural%20barriers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jagdish%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20most%20viable%20antidote%20would%20be%20the%20integration%20of%20diverse%20native%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3Edhau%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EAnogeissus%20pendula%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EButea%20monosperma%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20%3Cem%3Esalai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EBoswellia%20serrata%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20restore%20the%20ecological%20balance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20CATCH%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20for%20reforestation%20in%20the%20NSG%20campus%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20blueprint%20for%20building%20a%20forest%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20forest%2C%20having%20trees%20of%20varying%20heights%20is%20good%20from%20two%20standpoints%20%E2%80%94%20they%20support%20different%20species%2C%20and%20they%20influence%20different%20levels%20of%20light%20and%20water%20availability.%20The%20CATCH%20Foundation%20model%20is%20cognisant%20of%20this.%20It%20accounts%20for%20plants%20of%20every%20height%2C%20from%20shrub%20layers%20(6%20feet)%20to%20the%20canopy%20layers%20(above%2040%20feet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20steps%20of%20rewilding%20barren%20areas%20of%20land%20across%20India%20involve%20firstly%20narrowing%20down%20on%20areas%20which%20have%20been%20ridden%20by%20mining%20and%20de-forestation%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20steps%20of%20rewilding%20barren%20areas%20of%20land%20across%20India%20involve%20narrowing%20down%20areas%20which%20have%20been%20ridden%20by%20mining%20and%20deforestation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20inspection%20of%20the%20land%2C%20a%20land%20letter%20is%20acquired%20from%20the%20government.%20This%20documentation%20legally%20allows%20CATCH%20Foundation%20to%20lease%20the%20land%20and%20subject%20it%20to%20reforestation%20efforts.%20The%20next%20step%20is%20soil%20testing%20(and%20conducting%20a%20baseline%20survey%20of%20the%20site%20before%20plantation)%2C%20borewell%20digging%2C%20and%20then%20the%20creation%20of%20fencing%20systems%20to%20prevent%20any%20intervention%20from%20the%20local%20groups%20of%20domestic%20animals%20that%20might%20harm%20the%20plantation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CATCH%20team%20works%20on%20the%20project%20with%20post-plantation%20maintenance.%20They%20share%20that%20the%20team%20employs%20and%20trains%20local%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20ensures%20regular%20activities%20and%20ensures%20the%20forest%20is%20made%20self-sustainable%20in%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FByvdpRw4nMA%3Fsi%3DGdOmGtAyfjsgXeM6%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20integrating%20solar%20systems%20(in%20some%20cases)%20to%20harness%20green%20power%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20the%20forest%20grid-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20is%20the%20excavation%20stage%20where%20the%20land%20is%20prepared%20for%20plantation.%20Its%20productivity%20is%20enhanced%20with%20cow%20dung%20and%20rice%20husks%3B%20the%20latter%20is%20a%20dense%20source%20of%20carbon%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20water%20and%20nutrient-holding%20capacity%20of%20the%20soil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soil%20is%20mulched%20with%20agro-waste%20and%20then%20nourished%20with%20manure%20and%20vermicompost%2C%20which%20boost%20its%20nutrition%20quotient.%20What%20follows%20is%20the%20plantation%20activity.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20forest%20created%20by%20CATCH%20Foundation%20is%20a%20green%20oasis%20around%20which%20civilisation%20thrives.%20The%20foundation%20wishes%20to%20make%20forests%20mainstays%20in%20cities%20rather%20than%20fleeting%20inclusions.%20To%20ensure%20this%20permanence%2C%20there%20is%20a%20stringent%20assessment%20of%20these%20forests%20during%20the%20first%20three%20years.%20One%20of%20the%20main%20aims%20during%20this%20time%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20forest%20weed-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Catch%20Foundation%20does%20a%20routine%20maintenance%20of%20the%20forest%20for%20three%20years%20after%20which%20the%20forest%20is%20considered%20mature%20enough%20to%20thrive%20by%20itself%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418905%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECatch%20Foundation%20does%20routine%20maintenance%20of%20the%20forest%20for%20three%20years%2C%20after%20which%20the%20forest%20is%20considered%20mature%20enough%20to%20thrive%20by%20itself%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20forest%20is%20thriving%20without%20intervention%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20plenty.%20The%20most%20important%20of%20these%20is%20carbon%20sequestration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20mature%20tree%20can%20absorb%20around%2048%20pounds%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20per%20year.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20trees%20lower%20the%20ambient%20temperatures%2C%20creating%20a%20more%20comfortable%20microclimate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESparking%20a%20positive%20revolution%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20trees%20absorb%20excess%20water%2C%20these%20forests%20reduce%20surface%20runoff%2C%20thus%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20flooding%20in%20heavy%20rainfall%20events.%20This%20success%20is%20mirrored%20by%20the%20project%20at%20Vadodara%2C%20where%20L%26amp%3BT%20partnered%20with%20CATCH%20Foundation%20to%20create%20multiple%20forests%20with%2050%2C000%20trees%20in%20the%20Harni%20area%20of%20Vadodara.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20Shah%2C%20who%20leads%20CSR%20initiatives%20in%20the%20Vadodara%20region%20for%20L%26amp%3BT%20Energy%20Hydrocarbon%2C%20is%20fascinated%20by%20how%20tech-driven%20monitoring%20tools%20enabled%20them%20to%20track%20the%20health%20and%20growth%20of%20each%20forest%20patch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-10-1744205747.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20barren%20landscapes%20to%20lush%20forests%2C%20CATCH%20Foundation%20is%20bringing%20about%20a%20green%20revolution%20in%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.